{"word":"πάντῃ","slug":"πάντῃ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πάντῃ</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>πᾶς</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>every way, on every side</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>in every way, by all means, altogether, entirely</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}